title: Orbital-style progressive elec
caption: Orbital-style progressive electronic, 303 acid bassline with sawtooth resonance sweep, Roland TR-909 kick with tight low-end compression, hi-hats with 16th note shuffle pattern, Juno-60 poly pad with slow LFO filter modulation, arpeggiated Moog lead with portamento glide, subtle Oberheim strings, four-on-the-floor beat structure, side-chain pumping on pads, reverb sends on synths, 8-bar intro build, drop at bar 16
